    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163810/extras/007e93c38143cdd8fd113642d17caff9.avif?t=1697764747\" width=600 height=208 /></span><br>《死灵保安》官方QQ群：772378969<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >拿起法杖，安抚各路客人</h2>希望你的肌肉不是摆设，因为这里的客人都不好惹。小到街头混混，大到教会成员，一个草叉就能要你命。VIP房更是要重点“关照”，学着和客人们<strong>打成一片</strong>吧。<br>      <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163810/extras/a2f66ec04641083c6b89a0c8cc872a1d.poster.avif?t=1697764747\" width=616 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163810/extras/a2f66ec04641083c6b89a0c8cc872a1d.webm?t=1697764747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >换上制服，改变战斗能力</h2>每天上班前记得穿上帅气工装，变成你喜欢的模样。<strong>不同制服会赋予你不同的战斗方式和全新遗物</strong>。召唤丧尸、化作闪电、变身狂战士，每天上班都是新体验！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163810/extras/af7bdeb05631f0c64e29db93229f41c5.poster.avif?t=1697764747\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163810/extras/af7bdeb05631f0c64e29db93229f41c5.webm?t=1697764747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >250种道具与Build构筑</h2>你在店里捡到的每个遗物都能让你变得更强，走得更远，甚至引发意想不到的质变。不过嘛……你要是被客人打败了，那就要从头再来咯~<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163810/extras/8123065c9a899cff85045601b49ce289.poster.avif?t=1697764747\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163810/extras/8123065c9a899cff85045601b49ce289.webm?t=1697764747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163810/extras/8123065c9a899cff85045601b49ce289.mp4?t=1697764747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多变关卡，层层深入</h2>店里当然有特色主题房。等待复原归位的石柱房、需要祭品供奉的神像房、凭空召唤魔物的水晶房、考验操作的圣物狩猎房……咳咳，就是人类电视剧上常见的那些东西。以你的聪明才智，应付这些谜题应该绰绰有余吧？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163810/extras/72bb50d80a4e2e5b094ca595707c3d25.poster.avif?t=1697764747\" width=616 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163810/extras/72bb50d80a4e2e5b094ca595707c3d25.webm?t=1697764747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>“工资？那自然是不会亏待你的。记得下班前找我结清。<br>前提是见得到我的话，嘿嘿嘿（已黑化）。”<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163810/extras/4f47a7da95f50e24e69cf984ad1f0c1a.poster.avif?t=1697764747\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163810/extras/4f47a7da95f50e24e69cf984ad1f0c1a.webm?t=1697764747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163810/extras/4f47a7da95f50e24e69cf984ad1f0c1a.mp4?t=1697764747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
